Merrybet, Nigeria’s premium sports betting company is back with another edition of its foremost sports betting competition, the “Merrybet Punters League”. Customers have won millions of naira and various amazing gift prizes in past seasons of the competition. This new season is bigger and better with more categories for punters to win from and increased rewards for winners. Get paid for winning your bets. This edition of the Merrybet Punters League “With Us More Is Possible” is set to run for 6 months (December 1st, 2020 – May 30th, 2021) with weekly, monthly, quarterly rewards with the grand prize which would be won at the end of the 2020/2021 football season. These rewards are only available to customers of Merrybet Grand Prizes At The End Of The Season: 1st prize : ₦2,000,000 2nd prize: ₦1,000,000 3rd prize: ₦500,000 Quarterly Prizes: 1st prize: ₦500,000 2nd prize: ₦300,000 3rd prize: ₦200,000 Monthly Prizes: 1st prize: ₦300,000 2nd prize: ₦200,000 3rd prize: ₦100,000 Merrybet’s Chief Communications Officer of Merrybet, Mr. Lanre Odiase stated that the format of the competition was adjusted to allow for more winners in the various categories as the aim of the competition is for the organisation to reward its customers. To participate in the Merrybet Punters League, all you need to do is place bets with a minimum of ₦200 on soccer games on www.merrybet.com. The more bets you win, the more points you accumulate, and the higher your chances of winning. More information on the terms and conditions can be found on Merrybet. The last Merrybet Punters League competition “iPhone Giveaway” saw its top winning customers; Stanley Effiong – (M), Odunayo Bosede – (F), Abishua Tahbat – (M), Adebukola Babalola – (F), Tunde Juwon – (M), Akinyemi Makinde – (M) all win the latest iPhones. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-857636 size-large" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Image-of-previous-winners-780x1024.jpg" alt="" width="740" height="971" src